OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1774523168
OL,3,CFormer Google boss Matt Brittin
OL,4,Cannounced as new BBC director-general
OL,6,FFormer Google boss Matt Brittin has
OL,7,Fbeen announced as the next director-
OL,8,Fgeneral of the BBC.
OL,10,FThe 57-year-old spent almost two
OL,11,Fdecades at Google, rising to become
OL,12,Fthe company's president in Europe, the
OL,13,FMiddle East, and Africa.
OL,15,FThe announcement comes after the BBC's
OL,16,Fprevious director-general, Tim Davie,
OL,17,Fresigned late last year following
OL,18,Fcriticism over the way a speech by
OL,19,FDonald Trump was edited.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/4
