PN,31402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1774523168
OL,3,CFormer Google boss Matt Brittin
OL,4,Cannounced as new BBC director-general
OL,6,FDavie, along with former BBC News CEO
OL,7,FDeborah Turness, resigned in November
OL,8,F2025 after the corporation was accused
OL,9,Fof editorial bias against the US
OL,10,Fpresident.
OL,12,FThe broadcaster was accused of
OL,13,Fmisleading the public following claims
OL,14,Fthat the speech had been selectively
OL,15,Fedited in the documentary, Trump: A
OL,16,FSecond Chance?
OL,18,FThe episode broadcast in 2024 spliced
OL,19,Ftwo clips together from two separate
OL,20,Fparts of Trump's speech.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/4
