PN,31403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1774523168
OL,3,CFormer Google boss Matt Brittin
OL,4,Cannounced as new BBC director-general
OL,6,FThe BBC's appointment of a tech
OL,7,Fexecutive as director-general, rather
OL,8,Fthan someone with TV production and
OL,9,Fbroadcasting experience, marks a shift
OL,10,Ffor the corporation.
OL,12,FMr Brittin announced his departure
OL,13,Ffrom Google late last year.
OL,15,FHe is a non-executive director of the
OL,16,FGuardian Media Group board and, before
OL,17,Fjoining Google in 2007, spent time in
OL,18,Fmedia, marketing, and strategy,
OL,19,Fincluding as commercial director at
OL,20,FTrinity Mirror.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/4
