OL,3,CFormer Google boss Matt Brittin
OL,4,Cannounced as new BBC director-general
OL,6,FHe also served for nine years on the
OL,7,Fboard of Sainsbury's and has been a
OL,8,Ftrustee of charities including the
OL,9,FMedia Trust and the Climate Group.
